      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "――という訳で～\n{user}さんにも協力してほしいんだ～",
      "startTime": 4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "明後日のクリスマスライブで、琴乃の誕生日を\nサプライズでお祝いか。いいじゃないか",
      "startTime": 10.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "でしょ～？",
      "startTime": 14.4536730766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣達が暗躍していることは\n琴乃に気付かれないよう、俺も注意するよ",
      "startTime": 18.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "よろしく！\nでも暗躍って言い方はちょっと引っかかるな～",
      "startTime": 22.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣達が悪いことを企んでるみたいじゃない？",
      "startTime": 27.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣達はいいことするんだから！\n琴乃ちゃんのサンタさんになるんだよ！",
      "startTime": 35.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、悪かった\nもし俺で良かったら協力するよ。なんでも言ってくれ",
      "startTime": 40.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_06_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも？　本当に！？　{user}さん\nなんでもしてくれるの！？",
      "startTime": 47.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}